Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-weston-remote layer to the xxxx mailing list (xxxx@zzzz.org)
and cc: the maintainer:

Maintainer: Ron Munitz <ron@thepscg.com>

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-weston-remote layer to your build
